    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《开局五个亿》是一款超现实模拟经营类互动影像游戏，你将以主角的身份，完成启动资金五个亿的创业历程。在这场围绕金钱和爱情展开的冒险中，六位怀着各自目的，身份、类型各异的美女将参与到你的事业之中，当感情和事业相互交织，你将如何平衡与她们之间的关系？忙于创业的你又将如何选择？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >产品特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>真实创业体验，“事业”“爱情”双主线</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家将从五亿的启动资金开始，展开创业和恋爱的双重主线</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173890/extras/b269956eea6a429b5b7ebb2b1c6bfe27.poster.avif?t=1732184907\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173890/extras/b269956eea6a429b5b7ebb2b1c6bfe27.webm?t=1732184907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173890/extras/b269956eea6a429b5b7ebb2b1c6bfe27.mp4?t=1732184907\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据玩家投资决策，形成不同的财富收益，进而影响女主的感情结局</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173890/extras/4fd52d4893ec79e527ef306e3124471b.poster.avif?t=1732184907\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173890/extras/4fd52d4893ec79e527ef306e3124471b.webm?t=1732184907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173890/extras/4fd52d4893ec79e527ef306e3124471b.mp4?t=1732184907\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同于其他男频恋爱类互动影游，本游戏更注重模拟经营创业的真实过程，大量呈现了爱情和事业的两难选择，更贴近现实生活。 </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>超一线网红&amp;实力派演员携手，高质量创业心跳大冒险</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >梅宝莱，温心，陈思澈，李心爱，刘梦茹等实力派演员主演，花碎花，DJ江小白，牛奶公主小章，是你依然，詹妮Jenny，刘一琳，小玥玥，板板酱，Swan，车模土豆丝等知名网红主播参演。在游戏中她们将扮演或妩媚、或柔情、或无邪、或任性，亦或性感火热，高贵冷艳，性格迥异的美女，陪伴你的创业之路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >花费金钱不仅可以解锁和她们的专属剧情，甚至可以......签约她们成为你旗下公司的主播给你打工。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173890/extras/9de06dc6185e142afd9cd986a2c00923.poster.avif?t=1732184907\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173890/extras/9de06dc6185e142afd9cd986a2c00923.webm?t=1732184907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173890/extras/9de06dc6185e142afd9cd986a2c00923.mp4?t=1732184907\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>百余种故事分支，多条隐藏故事暗线与彩蛋</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >产品为您设计了百余种故事分支，多条隐藏故事暗线与彩蛋。“财富”和“情商”同样重要，通过正确的投资决策不断积累财富，才能更好地在游戏中收集各种成就、挖掘她们的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173890/extras/7661d4e638055be6448db2f13689b201.poster.avif?t=1732184907\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173890/extras/7661d4e638055be6448db2f13689b201.webm?t=1732184907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173890/extras/7661d4e638055be6448db2f13689b201.mp4?t=1732184907\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>做出最符合本心的选择，而不是最可能是正确的选择将为你带来意想不到的收获。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>“事业”亦是“爱情”，第一人称超现实互动恋爱体验</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏过程中随着主角财富值和事业的变化对应逐步揭示了演员不同阶段对角色内心世界的心路刻画。不同阶段下女主态度和对男主诉求的变化将影响玩家恋爱体验。而面对六位性格迥异的美女诱惑的你，将做出怎样的选择？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是表面单纯、对你无限崇拜的实习生？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173890/extras/1363c35b7ee5b09f98a85a7567358a3a.poster.avif?t=1732184907\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173890/extras/1363c35b7ee5b09f98a85a7567358a3a.webm?t=1732184907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是性感人妻、对你关怀备至的女邻居？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173890/extras/24e31feb2a1e6927950460dc4c29edf0.poster.avif?t=1732184907\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173890/extras/24e31feb2a1e6927950460dc4c29edf0.webm?t=1732184907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是傲娇明艳、性格多变的顶流女明星？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173890/extras/4762773ca2f9272057d8b174f713c62a.poster.avif?t=1732184907\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173890/extras/4762773ca2f9272057d8b174f713c62a.webm?t=1732184907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是理性至上、商业能力极强的女强人？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173890/extras/9869286b4d3326b5b8462b1dc6d10b66.poster.avif?t=1732184907\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173890/extras/9869286b4d3326b5b8462b1dc6d10b66.webm?t=1732184907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是甜美娇媚、新晋流量网红的初中同学？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173890/extras/aaec78901fe665ffd02e497b8fd087ea.poster.avif?t=1732184907\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173890/extras/aaec78901fe665ffd02e497b8fd087ea.webm?t=1732184907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还是金融精英、青梅竹马的美女合伙人？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173890/extras/dd250a00e89466adcbc50d28657f42aa.poster.avif?t=1732184907\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173890/extras/dd250a00e89466adcbc50d28657f42aa.webm?t=1732184907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与你心仪的她，分享创业路上的成就与烦恼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>PS：本游戏在剧情中穿插了超过100余个映射原型事件的“梗”，不仅有“娱乐梗”和“事件梗”更有部分“专业梗”期待玩家们自行挖掘。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >开发者的话</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      在当下恋爱类影游横行，架空故事满天飞的时候，我们选择了另一种更现实也更贴近生活的呈现方式。很多人都幻想过，如果自己很有钱一定也会很成功，会拥有豪车、豪宅，身边美女如云，会想着如果有钱，一定能投中独角兽，躺着就能赚到更多的钱…… 可是实际情况绝不仅于此，创业和投资对所有人都是公平的，现实远比想象的更加艰难，没有时间上的付出你将很难收获事业上的成功。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      本款游戏会将真实的创业投资以尽量简单有趣的模拟经营方式让玩家进行体验。在众多投资项目中，如何做出最明智的决策？在女主碰到困难的时候如何帮助？该投入多少钱？值不值得？如何把兴趣爱好干成成功的事业？这都是我们想呈现给玩家的游戏感受，我们在做这款游戏的时候，加入了更多对于真实商业和人性变化的思考，这款游戏，就是希望能让更多人体验创业的艰辛和现实的残酷。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      拥有了金钱就是拥有了加入战场的武器，但是输赢，有的时候的确是需要一些运气和努力，天时地利人和，缺一不可。当然，在这些真实的创业体验中，六位美女的相伴也是我们给玩家的绝美福利，她们不仅是玩家的情绪价值给予者，更是玩家创业过程中的鲜明对照。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最后，希望玩家们多踩一些游戏中的雷，从而避开一些现实中的雷，都能在自己的生活里获得完美开局！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢迎关注官方账号，获取最新情报福利</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方QQ 1群：1005779185 (已满)<br>官方QQ 2群：826706420 （推荐）</p>",
